        Social Proof for Dog Walkers
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Hiring someone to walk their dog isn't a casual decision for most pet owners — they're handing over their family member to a stranger. Your testimonials from other pet parents are what turn that hesitation into a booking.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Pet owners need to see proof of care</h2>
